### Create customer profile
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john@lorettabank.co.za",
  "phoneNumber": "+27821234567",
  "idNumber": "9501015800089",
  "dateOfBirth": "1995-01-01",
  "address": "123 Main Street, Cape Town, 8001"
}

### Get my customer profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get customer by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update customer
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+27821234568",
  "address": "456 New Street, Johannesburg, 2000"
}

### Update KYC status (admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers/1/kyc?status=VERIFIED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### List customers (admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
